Class Road

java.lang.Object
Road
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Road>
public class Road extends Object implements Comparable<Road>
This Road class represents the edges of a Graph of Towns. This class will store the references to the two vertices(town endpoints), the distance of vertices, and the name. This class will also implement the comparable interface

Lima Waziri
